## 5. DATABASE STRUCTURE

### 5.1 Core Tables

**Company Structure:**
- `company_profile` - Organization information
- `branches` - Branch office details
- `departments` - Department structure
- `job_positions` - Position definitions
- `employment_types` - Employment categories

**Employee Management:**
- `employees` - Master employee data
- `employee_contracts` - Contract information
- `probation_records` - Probation tracking
- `former_employees` - Ex-employee archive
- `employee_documents` - Document storage

**Asset Management:**
- `asset_categories` - Asset classification
- `assets` - Asset registry
- `asset_assignments` - Assignment tracking

**Talent Acquisition:**
- `job_vacancies` - Job postings
- `applicants` - Candidate information
- `interviews` - Interview tracking

**Attendance & Leave:**
- `attendance_records` - Daily attendance
- `shift_schedules` - Shift definitions
- `leave_types` - Leave categories
- `leave_requests` - Leave applications
- `leave_balances` - Leave entitlements

**Performance:**
- `performance_reviews` - Review records
- `feedback_360` - 360-degree feedback
- `training_records` - Training history

**System:**
- `users` - System users
- `roles` - User roles
- `permissions` - Access permissions
- `audit_logs` - Activity tracking

### 5.2 Database Features
- Foreign key constraints for referential integrity
- Comprehensive audit trails
- Soft delete implementation
- Optimized indexing strategy
- Transaction support for data consistency

---

## 6. SECURITY FEATURES

### 6.1 Authentication & Authorization
- Secure session management
- Multi-factor authentication support
- Role-based access control (RBAC)
- Granular permission system
- Password strength requirements

### 6.2 Data Protection
- Input validation and sanitization
- SQL injection prevention
- XSS protection
- CSRF token validation
- Encrypted sensitive data storage

### 6.3 Audit & Compliance
- Comprehensive activity logging
- Change tracking
- Data access monitoring
- Regulatory compliance features
- Report generation for audits

### 6.4 Session Security
- Inactivity timeout (15 minutes)
- Session hardening
- Secure cookie configuration
- Automatic logout on inactivity
- Session fixation prevention

